  - getNumberOfElements(MED_NODE,MED_NONE) : number of nodes
  - getNumberOfElements(MED_NODE,MED_TRIA3) : returns 0 (not defined)
  - getNumberOfElements(MED_FACE,MED_TRIA3) : returns number of triangle
